query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
account_id as "account_id!: String", 
username as "username!: String", 
user_id as "user_id!: String", 
status as "status!: HandleStatus", 
created_at as "created_at!: DateTime < Utc >", 
force_hydrate as "force_hydrate!: bool", 
total_collabs as "total_collabs!: i32", 
total_collab_rewards as "total_collab_rewards!: String", 
x_refresh_token as "x_refresh_token!: Option < String >", 
invalidated_x_refresh_token as "invalidated_x_refresh_token!: Option < String >", 
score as "score!: Option < String >", 
last_scoring as "last_scoring!: Option < UtcDateTime >", 
current_scoring_id as "current_scoring_id!: Option < i32 >", 
online_engagement_override as "online_engagement_override!: Option < EngagementScore >", 
online_engagement_override_reason as "online_engagement_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
offline_engagement_score as "offline_engagement_score!: EngagementScore", 
offline_engagement_description as "offline_engagement_description!: Option < String >", 
poll_id as "poll_id!: Option < String >", 
poll_ends_at as "poll_ends_at!: Option < DateTime < Utc > >", 
poll_override as "poll_override!: Option < PollScore >", 
poll_override_reason as "poll_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
operational_status_override as "operational_status_override!: Option < OperationalStatus >", 
operational_status_override_reason as "operational_status_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
referrer_score_override as "referrer_score_override!: Option < bool >", 
referrer_score_override_reason as "referrer_score_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
holder_score_override as "holder_score_override!: Option < bool >", 
holder_score_override_reason as "holder_score_override_reason!: Option < String >", 
audience_size_override as "audience_size_override!: Option < i32 >", 
audience_size_override_reason as "audience_size_override_reason!: Option < String >" FROM handles WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR account_id = $6::varchar) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR username = $8::varchar) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR username LIKE $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR username ILIKE $12::varchar) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR user_id = $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR user_id LIKE $16::varchar) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR status = $18::handle_status) AND (NOT $19::boolean OR status = ANY(CAST($20 as handle_status[])) ) AND (NOT $21::boolean OR created_at = $22::timestamptz) AND (NOT $23::boolean OR created_at > $24::timestamptz) AND (NOT $25::boolean OR force_hydrate = $26::boolean) AND (NOT $27::boolean OR total_collabs = $28::int4) AND (NOT $29::boolean OR total_collab_rewards = $30::varchar) AND (NOT $31::boolean OR x_refresh_token = $32::text) AND ($33::boolean IS NULL OR (($33::boolean AND x_refresh_token IS NOT NULL) OR (NOT $33::boolean AND x_refresh_token IS NULL))) AND (NOT $34::boolean OR invalidated_x_refresh_token = $35::text) AND ($36::boolean IS NULL OR (($36::boolean AND invalidated_x_refresh_token IS NOT NULL) OR (NOT $36::boolean AND invalidated_x_refresh_token IS NULL))) AND (NOT $37::boolean OR score = $38::varchar) AND (NOT $39::boolean OR last_scoring = $40::timestamptz) AND (NOT $41::boolean OR current_scoring_id = $42::int4) AND (NOT $43::boolean OR online_engagement_override = $44::engagement_score) AND (NOT $45::boolean OR online_engagement_override_reason = $46::text) AND (NOT $47::boolean OR offline_engagement_score = $48::engagement_score) AND (NOT $49::boolean OR offline_engagement_description = $50::text) AND (NOT $51::boolean OR poll_id = $52::varchar) AND (NOT $53::boolean OR poll_ends_at = $54::timestamptz) AND (NOT $55::boolean OR poll_override = $56::poll_score) AND (NOT $57::boolean OR poll_override_reason = $58::varchar) AND (NOT $59::boolean OR operational_status_override = $60::operational_status) AND (NOT $61::boolean OR operational_status_override_reason = $62::text) AND (NOT $63::boolean OR referrer_score_override = $64::boolean) AND (NOT $65::boolean OR referrer_score_override_reason = $66::text) AND (NOT $67::boolean OR holder_score_override = $68::boolean) AND (NOT $69::boolean OR holder_score_override_reason = $70::text) AND (NOT $71::boolean OR audience_size_override = $72::int4) AND (NOT $73::boolean OR audience_size_override_reason = $74::text) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($75 = 'Id' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'Id' AND $76) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'AccountId' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN account_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'AccountId' AND $76) WHEN true THEN account_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'Username' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN username ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'Username' AND $76) WHEN true THEN username ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'UserId' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN user_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'UserId' AND $76) WHEN true THEN user_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'Status' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'Status' AND $76) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'CreatedAt' AND $76) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'ForceHydrate' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN force_hydrate ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'ForceHydrate' AND $76) WHEN true THEN force_hydrate ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'TotalCollabs' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN total_collabs ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'TotalCollabs' AND $76) WHEN true THEN total_collabs ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'TotalCollabRewards' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN total_collab_rewards ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'TotalCollabRewards' AND $76) WHEN true THEN total_collab_rewards ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'XRefreshToken' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN x_refresh_token ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'XRefreshToken' AND $76) WHEN true THEN x_refresh_token ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'InvalidatedXRefreshToken' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN invalidated_x_refresh_token ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'InvalidatedXRefreshToken' AND $76) WHEN true THEN invalidated_x_refresh_token ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'Score' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN score ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'Score' AND $76) WHEN true THEN score ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'LastScoring' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN last_scoring ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'LastScoring' AND $76) WHEN true THEN last_scoring ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'CurrentScoringId' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN current_scoring_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'CurrentScoringId' AND $76) WHEN true THEN current_scoring_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OnlineEngagementOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN online_engagement_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OnlineEngagementOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN online_engagement_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OnlineEngagementOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN online_engagement_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OnlineEngagementOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN online_engagement_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OfflineEngagementScore' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN offline_engagement_score ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OfflineEngagementScore' AND $76) WHEN true THEN offline_engagement_score ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OfflineEngagementDescription' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN offline_engagement_description ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OfflineEngagementDescription' AND $76) WHEN true THEN offline_engagement_description ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollId' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN poll_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollId' AND $76) WHEN true THEN poll_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollEndsAt' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN poll_ends_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollEndsAt' AND $76) WHEN true THEN poll_ends_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN poll_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN poll_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN poll_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'PollOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN poll_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OperationalStatusOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN operational_status_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OperationalStatusOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN operational_status_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'OperationalStatusOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN operational_status_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'OperationalStatusOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN operational_status_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'ReferrerScoreOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN referrer_score_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'ReferrerScoreOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN referrer_score_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'ReferrerScoreOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN referrer_score_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'ReferrerScoreOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN referrer_score_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'HolderScoreOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN holder_score_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'HolderScoreOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN holder_score_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'HolderScoreOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN holder_score_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'HolderScoreOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN holder_score_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'AudienceSizeOverride' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN audience_size_override ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'AudienceSizeOverride' AND $76) WHEN true THEN audience_size_override ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($75 = 'AudienceSizeOverrideReason' AND NOT $76) WHEN true THEN audience_size_override_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($75 = 'AudienceSizeOverrideReason' AND $76) WHEN true THEN audience_size_override_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $77 OFFSET $78 FOR UPDATE
